          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Energy spectrum of photons produced in the reaction",
                "Li-6(gamma,xgamma') is studied at bremsstrahlung",
                "end-point energy of 32 MeV. A gamma-line at 2.22 MeV",
                "has been observed in the spectrum. This line is shown",
                "not to be related to the background radiative capture",
                "reaction n+p. The width of the 2.22-MeV gamma-line is",
                "25(5) keV. The integral population cross section equals",
                " (1.2(0.3))*10**(-3) MeV*mb.Because the spectrum of the",
                "residual nuclei does not contain the 2.22 MeV state,",
                "one may attribute the maximum to the peculiarities of",
                "the reaction mechanism."
              ]
            }
          ],
